{"tid":1290852,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人: 香港已經不是香港了","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T11:26:14.000Z","uid":64153,"like":135,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"284ca9cb7bd22a6989a4661c92616ef02ba3490e","tid":1290852,"uid":64153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"小弟去左高雄旅行<br />\n係旗津搭船翻去西子灣個陣<br />\n聽到隔離一對夫妻嘅對話<br />\n妻: 夜景好美呀 簡直是維多利亞港<br />\n夫: 可是香港已經不是香港了<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度<br />\n小弟個下啲眼淚真一下子咁想湧出黎<br />\n連外國人都比某部分香港人清楚<br />\n呢個地方已經被改變得太多了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678814d65eca083a37cc86f65c6c4f3e1498ebf3","tid":1290852,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"起咗雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74cecc87978cb1045b2989cd80f21291557595a","tid":1290852,"uid":50502,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"經歷完咁多事 先發覺到香港原來有200萬同路人 市民修養係咁好<br />\n但將來香港政府只會愈黎愈赤化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e096b37175a90bacc88115ce8d43df7ae2c081a0","tid":1290852,"uid":64153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"678814d65eca083a37cc86f65c6c4f3e1498ebf3","tid":1290852,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"起咗雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"個下<br />\n真係個心即刻沉左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78076c41f7889085658c4df59816c92e8fb8b13","tid":1290852,"uid":64153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f74cecc87978cb1045b2989cd80f21291557595a","tid":1290852,"uid":50502,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"r